Extra Virgin Americana - Season 1, Episode 3




A San Francisco Pop-Up Treat

The family is headed to Napa Valley to throw a pop-up party at a friend's vineyard. They stop in San Francisco on the way, grabbing some salumi for the pop-up and eating at a porchetta stand at the Farmers' Market. Debi Mazar and Gabriele Corcos get the pop-up ready at the vineyard while Robert and the girls explore San Francisco, before it's time for their mouthwatering family-style meal.




Original Air Date: 16-Mar-2016
